OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779516361
OL,3,CTraffic jams, rail disruption and busy
OL,4,Cports: bank holiday getaway begins
OL,6,FRoads to popular tourist destinations
OL,7,Fare expected to become congested and
OL,8,Fthe port of Dover is preparing for the
OL,9,Fbusiest day of the year so far, as the
OL,10,Fbank holiday getaway begins.
OL,12,FIn addition, strike action and
OL,13,Fengineering work will cause disruption
OL,14,Fon a number of routes on Britain's
OL,15,Frailways.
OL,17,FThe AA has estimated 23.4 million car
OL,18,Fjourneys will take place on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
