OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779516361
OL,3,CTraffic jams, rail disruption and busy
OL,4,Cports: bank holiday getaway begins
OL,6,FIt highlighted likely traffic
OL,7,Fblackspots to include routes heading
OL,8,Ftowards east coast destinations such
OL,9,Fas Skegness, the M4 from London
OL,10,Ftowards Wales, and the M6 towards the
OL,11,Fnorth-west coast.
OL,13,FThe RAC expects leisure traffic to
OL,14,Fpeak on Friday and Saturday.
OL,16,FThe Port of Dover in Kent, which is
OL,17,Fpreparing for 18,000 travellers
OL,18,Fbetween Friday and Sunday, warned the
OL,19,Fbusiest periods each day will be
OL,20,Fbetween 6am and about 1pm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
