PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779516361
OL,3,CTraffic jams, rail disruption and busy
OL,4,Cports: bank holiday getaway begins
OL,6,FSaturday will be the port's busiest
OL,7,Fday of the year so far, with more than
OL,8,F8,000 travellers.
OL,10,FStrike action and engineering work
OL,11,Fwill cause disruption on a number of
OL,12,Froutes on Britain's railways.
OL,14,FWalkouts by members of the Transport
OL,15,FSalaried Staffs' Association on Friday
OL,16,Fand Saturday in a dispute over pay
OL,17,Fwill affect West Midlands Railway
OL,18,F(WMR) and London Northwestern Railway
OL,19,Fservices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
