PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779516361
OL,3,CTraffic jams, rail disruption and busy
OL,4,Cports: bank holiday getaway begins
OL,6,FTimetables will be slashed on both
OL,7,Fdays, including no WMT trains after
OL,8,F7pm on Friday or before 7am on
OL,9,FSaturday.
OL,11,FNetwork Rail engineering work means
OL,12,Fparts of key intercity lines will be
OL,13,Fshut.
OL,15,FThe East Coast Main Line will be
OL,16,Fclosed between York and Darlington
OL,17,Ffrom Saturday through to Monday.
OL,19,FBuses will replace trains between
OL,20,FNewport and Bristol Parkway from
OL,21,FSaturday for two weeks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
