PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779516361
OL,3,CTraffic jams, rail disruption and busy
OL,4,Cports: bank holiday getaway begins
OL,6,FThere will be no Thameslink services
OL,7,Fthrough central London between
OL,8,FSaturday and Monday, affecting
OL,9,Fservices to Gatwick and Luton airports.
OL,11,FTravel trade organisation Abta said
OL,12,Fthere will be a surge in families
OL,13,Fheading off on holiday this weekend as
OL,14,Fit marks the start of half-term breaks
OL,15,Ffor many schools.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
