OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779516361
OL,3,CTraffic jams, rail disruption and busy
OL,4,Cports: bank holiday getaway begins
OL,6,FIt reported strong demand for short-
OL,7,Fhaul sunshine holidays in destinations
OL,8,Fsuch as mainland Spain, Italy, the
OL,9,FBalearic and Canary Islands, and
OL,10,FPortugal, as well as city breaks in
OL,11,FMilan, Nice and Barcelona.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, parking app company RingGo
OL,14,Fsaid its analysis of recent bank
OL,15,Fholiday periods found Saturday is
OL,16,Flikely to be the busiest day of the
OL,17,Flong weekend at coastal towns and
OL,18,Fcities such as Bournemouth, Hastings
OL,19,Fand Torquay.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
