PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779516361
OL,3,CTraffic jams, rail disruption and busy
OL,4,Cports: bank holiday getaway begins
OL,6,FIt said seaside towns are
OL,7,F"consistently outperforming inland
OL,8,Flocations" during bank holidays in
OL,9,Fterms of the number of parking
OL,10,Fsessions recorded.
OL,12,FThe Met Office has forecast a heatwave
OL,13,Fin some parts this weekend.
OL,15,FTemperatures are set to peak on Monday
OL,16,Fwhen 33C could be recorded in southern
OL,17,FEngland and the Midlands.
